OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften large amounts of cloud,
OL,6,Fbut still bright or sunny spells will
OL,7,Foccur, especially later this
OL,8,Fafternoon, with all areas remaining
OL,9,Fdry. Feeling warm or very warm in the
OL,10,Flight winds away from cooling onshore
OL,11,Fbreezes along the south coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry and becoming largely
OL,14,Fclear, although late in the night low
OL,15,Fcloud may creep across parts of
OL,16,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight, while
OL,17,Fpatchy mist may develop elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
