OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry and warm or very warm,
OL,6,Fdespite large amounts of cloud quickly
OL,7,Fspreading east. Still, some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells will occur. Breezy at
OL,9,Ftimes, especially along the south
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBreezy
OL,13,Fat times with variable cloud for much
OL,14,Fof the period, staying mostly dry with
OL,15,Fhazy sunshine at times. Temperatures
OL,16,Flikely above average, becoming very
OL,17,Fwarm or hot in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
